      "model_answer": "根据提供的源码片段和上下文，FastAPI 中的 `get` 是 `FastAPI` 类的一个方法，用于注册 HTTP GET 请求的路由。\n\n### 定义位置\n- **文件名**: `fastapi/applications.py`\n- **行号**: 大约在第 300-350 行之间（具体行号可能因版本略有差异，但通常在 `FastAPI` 类的 `get` 方法定义处）\n\n### 参数列表\n```python\ndef get(\n    self,\n    path: Annotated[\n        str,\n        Doc(\"\"\"The path to the operation.\"\"\")\n    ],\n    *,\n    response_model: Annotated[\n        Any,\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    status_code: Annotated[\n        Optional[int],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    tags: Annotated[\n        Optional[List[str]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    dependencies: Annotated[\n        Optional[Sequence[Depends]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    summary: Annotated[\n        Optional[str],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    description: Annotated[\n        Optional[str],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    response_description: Annotated[\n        str,\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = \"Successful Response\",\n    responses: Annotated[\n        Optional[Dict[Union[int, str], Dict[str, Any]]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    deprecated: Annotated[\n        Optional[bool],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    operation_id: Annotated[\n        Optional[str],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    response_model_include: Annotated[\n        Optional[Set[str]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    response_model_exclude: Annotated[\n        Optional[Set[str]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    response_model_by_alias: Annotated[\n        bool,\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = True,\n    response_model_exclude_unset: Annotated[\n        bool,\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = False,\n    response_model_exclude_defaults: Annotated[\n        bool,\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = False,\n    response_model_exclude_none: Annotated[\n        bool,\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = False,\n    include_in_schema: Annotated[\n        bool,\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = True,\n    response_class: Annotated[\n        Optional[Type[Response]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    name: Annotated[\n        Optional[str],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    callbacks: Annotated[\n        Optional[List[BaseRoute]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    openapi_extra: Annotated[\n        Optional[Dict[str, Any]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n    generate_unique_id_function: Annotated[\n        Optional[Callable[[APIRoute], str]],\n        Doc(\"\"\"...\"\"\")\n    ] = None,\n) -> Callable[[DecoratedCallable], DecoratedCallable]:\n```\n\n### 主要职责\n`get` 方法的主要职责是：\n1. **注册路由**：将指定的 `path` 与 HTTP GET 方法绑定，并注册到 FastAPI 应用的路由表中。\n2. **配置端点**：通过参数（如 `response_model`、`status_code`、`tags`、`dependencies` 等）配置该端点的行为、文档和验证规则。\n3. **返回装饰器**：返回一个装饰器函数，用于装饰实际处理该 GET 请求的 Python 异步函数（或同步函数）。\n4. **内部调用**：最终调用 `self.api_route` 方法（定义在 `fastapi/applications.py` 中），该方法会创建 `APIRoute` 对象并添加到路由列表。\n\n### 调用链\n```\nFastAPI.get()\n  -> self.api_route(path=path, methods=[\"GET\"], ...)\n    -> self.router.add_api_route(path, endpoint, methods=[\"GET\"], ...)\n      -> APIRoute(path, endpoint, methods=[\"GET\"], ...)\n        -> self.routes.append(route)\n```\n\n### 关键点\n- `get` 是 `FastAPI` 类的一个便捷方法，实际底层调用 `api_route` 方法。\n- 所有参数都是可选的（除了 `path`），用于控制 OpenAPI 文档生成、数据验证、响应模型等。\n- 返回类型是一个装饰器，用于装饰视图函数。",
