      "model_answer": "根据提供的源码片段和 FastAPI 的常见实现，`head` 是 `FastAPI` 类的一个方法，用于注册处理 HTTP HEAD 请求的路由。\n\n- **定义文件**：`fastapi/applications.py`\n- **行号**：通常在 `FastAPI` 类中，`head` 方法定义在 `get`、`post` 等方法附近，具体行号可能因版本略有不同，但一般在 300-400 行之间（以 FastAPI 0.100.0 为例，大约在 350 行左右）。\n- **参数列表**：\n  ```python\n  def head(\n      self,\n      path: Annotated[\n          str,\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              The path to the endpoint.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ],\n      *,\n      response_model: Annotated[\n          Optional[Type[Any]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              The response model to use for the endpoint.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      status_code: Annotated[\n          Optional[int],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              The status code to use for the endpoint.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      tags: Annotated[\n          Optional[List[Union[str, Enum]]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              A list of tags to be applied to the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      dependencies: Annotated[\n          Optional[Sequence[Depends]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              A list of dependencies to be applied to the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      summary: Annotated[\n          Optional[str],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              A summary for the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      description: Annotated[\n          Optional[str],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              A description for the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      response_description: Annotated[\n          str,\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              The description for the response.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = \"Successful Response\",\n      responses: Annotated[\n          Optional[Dict[Union[int, str], Dict[str, Any]]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Additional responses to show in the OpenAPI schema.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      deprecated: Annotated[\n          Optional[bool],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Mark the path operation as deprecated.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      operation_id: Annotated[\n          Optional[str],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Unique identifier for the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      response_model_include: Annotated[\n          Optional[Set[Union[int, str]]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Fields to include in the response model.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      response_model_exclude: Annotated[\n          Optional[Set[Union[int, str]]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Fields to exclude from the response model.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      response_model_by_alias: Annotated[\n          bool,\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Whether to use field aliases in the response model.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = True,\n      response_model_exclude_unset: Annotated[\n          bool,\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Whether to exclude unset fields from the response model.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = False,\n      response_model_exclude_defaults: Annotated[\n          bool,\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Whether to exclude default fields from the response model.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = False,\n      response_model_exclude_none: Annotated[\n          bool,\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Whether to exclude None fields from the response model.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = False,\n      include_in_schema: Annotated[\n          bool,\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Whether to include the path operation in the OpenAPI schema.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = True,\n      response_class: Annotated[\n          Optional[Type[Response]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              The response class to use for the endpoint.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      name: Annotated[\n          Optional[str],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              A name for the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      callbacks: Annotated[\n          Optional[List[BaseRoute]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              A list of callbacks to be applied to the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      openapi_extra: Annotated[\n          Optional[Dict[str, Any]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              Extra OpenAPI fields to add to the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n      generate_unique_id_function: Annotated[\n          Optional[Callable[[APIRoute], str]],\n          Doc(\"\"\"\n              A function to generate unique IDs for the path operation.\n          \"\"\"),\n      ] = None,\n  ) -> Callable[[DecoratedCallable], DecoratedCallable]:\n  ```\n- **主要职责**：`head` 方法用于注册一个处理 HTTP HEAD 请求的路由。它内部会调用 `self.api_route` 方法，并将 `methods=[\"HEAD\"]` 作为参数传递，从而将装饰的函数绑定到指定的路径和 HEAD 方法上。该方法返回一个装饰器，用于装饰实际处理请求的函数。",
